2e10437899fd836b9c9d5c42ec9715cf94af54cea09a3649172b5d7497a378fdf292ba87a2eedf0b26413499a06ef03b51ea7edb31e8a37a05970823d90a10e1  0003-QtKeyExtensionGlobal-fix-export.patch"
